            "body": "Since we are ultimately passing to the LSP positions within the buffer, rather than controlling the cursor position like `vim.diagnostic.jump`, using `vim.pos` is more accurate. I am converting this PR to a draft until `vim.pos` moves out of the experimental stage.",
